A hired front line soldier mustn’t rush to battle.

66
00:03:51,860 --> 00:03:54,020
‐That’s quite the bold statement sir.

67
00:03:54,340 --> 00:03:55,520
[chuckles menacingly]

68
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:57,000
‐I told you.

69
00:03:57,110 --> 00:03:58,650
I am a true soldier.

70
00:04:06,300 --> 00:04:07,920
<i>Heero Yuy: All areas functioning.</i>

71
