79
00:04:39,020 --> 00:04:41,260
‐I'm sorry I couldn’t spend much time with you.

80
00:04:41,260 --> 00:04:43,760
But I'm afraid my work keeps getting in the way.

81
00:04:44,020 --> 00:04:46,000
‐Father, next time we go out to space...

82
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:48,700
...how about leaving yourself a little bit of free time?

83
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:51,620
Huh? Father, what is that?

84
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:55,460
<i>‐Heero: Relative speed to target, 01545.</i>

85
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:58,050
Engaging auto lock.

86
00:04:58,110 --> 00:05:00,380
Ready to shoot the obstacle down.

87
00:05:00,380 --> 00:05:02,680
[enemy alert]

88
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:04,720
<i>Earth’s assault carrier?!</i>

89
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:08,050
‐We’ve caught up.

90
00:05:08,110 --> 00:05:09,340
I'll bring it up on screen.

91
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:12,400
‐Just as I thought.

92
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:14,500
So thats their little "battle seed"...

93
00:05:14,500 --> 00:05:18,120
...all ready to sprout into new battles.

94
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:19,700
‐Operation M.

95
