he’s on a secret mission,

102
00:05:33,310 --> 00:05:34,680
you have to remember.

103
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,860
The Alliance is already on to me.

104
00:05:37,300 --> 00:05:38,380
Dammit.

105
00:05:41,620 --> 00:05:43,050
<i>‐Pilot 1: He’s entered the atmosphere;</i>

106
00:05:43,140 --> 00:05:44,220
<i>we’ll follow.</i>

107
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:46,700
I'm finally here.

108
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,900
I've made it to Earth.

109
