‐But the capsule’s increasing speed.

114
00:06:06,220 --> 00:06:07,680
He’s trying to break away.

115
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:09,370
‐How could he?

116
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:11,480
There’s no way he could survive that heat!

117
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:13,110
‐Not necessarily.

118
00:06:13,110 --> 00:06:17,200
Obviously our enemies are very technologically advanced.

119
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:22,060
‐Atmosphere entry capsule?

120
00:06:22,060 --> 00:06:24,080
‐Operation Meteor!

121
00:06:24,080 --> 00:06:24,980
‐Huh?

122
00:06:33,910 --> 00:06:41,740
