123
00:06:46,140 --> 00:06:48,380
<i>‐Pilot 2: Lieutenant Zechs, what is this?</i>

124
00:06:48,380 --> 00:06:50,740
<i>‐Zechs: The enemy's new weapon is a fighter.</i>

125
00:06:51,840 --> 00:06:53,900
<i>‐Pilot 1: It moves just like a bird.</i>

126
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:55,480
<i>‐We’ve reached flight altitude.</i>

127
00:06:55,540 --> 00:06:56,770
<i>We can proceed to attack.</i>

128
00:06:58,280 --> 00:07:00,560
