130
00:07:01,370 --> 00:07:02,910
<i>No machine gun for him.</i>

131
00:07:03,020 --> 00:07:04,580
<i>Shoot him down!</i>

132
00:07:04,580 --> 00:07:06,100
‐But Lieutenant Zechs.

133
