Roger that mission.

142
00:07:34,460 --> 00:07:37,740
I’ll return right now to shoot down the OZ carrier.

143
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:40,140
‐Enemy fighter has turned around

144
00:07:40,170 --> 00:07:41,680
