148
00:07:46,580 --> 00:07:47,800
<i>‐You guessed it.</i>

149
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:50,300
<i>‐Then wouldn’t the Aries Lightspeed mobile suit...</i>

150
00:07:50,300 --> 00:07:52,460
