154
00:08:01,580 --> 00:08:02,720
<i>‐Lieutenant Zechs,</i>

155
00:08:02,780 --> 00:08:04,880
<i>I’ll send backup as soon as Aries is ready.</i>

156
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:06,700
<i>‐Roger!</i>

157
00:08:07,100 --> 00:08:08,440
What the?! He’s above!

158
